# FindGLFW3
# ------------
#
# Locate glfw3 library
#
# This module defines
#
# ::
#
#   GLFW3_LIBRARIES, the library to link against
#   GLFW3_FOUND, if false, do not try to link to FREETYPE
#   GLFW3_INCLUDE_DIRS, where to find headers.
#   This is the concatenation of the paths:
#   GLFW3_INCLUDE_DIR
